- [ ] Output (stdout/stderr) correctly captured
- [ ] Exit codes correctly propagated
- [ ] Environment and cwd work correctly
- [ ] Timeouts and signals handled
- [ ] ALL phases logged with structured JSON","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:24:16.045008068Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-19T19:04:01.910661983Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mnaa","depends_on_id":"bd-255k","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:24:29.871020239Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-mnaa","depends_on_id":"bd-2bid","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:24:31.282038595Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
